data.title: Jovanovic: The excitement and assurance are the motto of derby matches we are ready to win
data.meta_description: Ivan Jovanovic, our first football team coach, said that the derby has always been exciting and from the first moment, and the match against Shabab Al Ahli in the 11th round of the Arabian Gulf League will certainly be one of the most important games of the season, in which we seek to win and reduce the difference with the teams ahead.
data.text:
Ivan Jovanovic, our first football team coach, said that the derby has always been exciting and from the first moment, and the match against Shabab Al Ahli in the 11th round of the Arabian Gulf League will certainly be one of the most important games of the season, in which we seek to win and reduce the difference with the teams ahead.

He added, "After the return of all the players, the competition between them on all levels is healthy and in the interest of the team and I am happy with the availibility of players in all positions, Al Nasr is a big team and all the major teams always have more than a strong and influential alternative."

He added that, "It is an opportunity for all youth to offer their best players, Derby matches are called games for players, personal motivations in addition to the motivation and preparation of the technical staff before these types of games are at their peak and I hope that affects our players positively and impose their words in the upcoming match. "

For his part, Massoud Sulaiman said, "the derby game is a good opportunity for Al Nasr to win and return to the track of the victories that missed the team in the previous round against Bani Yas."

He added, "Al Nasr is not far from the competition for the title, the points difference can be compensated in the next games, the determination of the players and their desire to continue the positive results will be the key to winning in all matches"
